       DETAIL
*           CONVERT BETWEEN MAD AND FORTRAN INTEGERS  
       LBL     FINT
       ENTRY   FINT     
       ENTRY   MINT     
       REM     FINT CONVERTS MAD INTEGERS TO FORTRAN INTEGERS     
FINT   CLA*    1,4           GET ARGUMENT 
       LDQ     =0 
       LRS     15            THIS SHOULD BE ENTIRE INTEGER  
       TNZ     *+3
       LLS     33            PUT INTEGER IN DECR. OF AC     
       TRA     2,4
       REM     INTEGER TOO LARGE FOR DECREMENT. TRUNCATE AND WRITE
       REM          ERROR MESSAGE BEFORE RETURN.
       STQ     MQ            SAVE RIGHTMOST 15 BITS.  
       SXA     XR4,4    
       TSX     $WRFLX,4 
       PZE     MSG1,,5  
XR4    AXT     **,4     
       CLA     MQ            INTEGER RETURNED IS RIGHTMOST 15 BITS
       ARS     2             OF ORIGINAL INTEGER BUT IN DECREMENT.
       TRA     2,4
MQ     PZE  
MSG1   BCI     5,MAD INTEGER EXCEEDS 32767.     
       REM     MINT CONVERTS FORTRAN INTEGERS TO MAD INTEGERS     
MINT   CLA*    1,4
       ARS     18 
       TRA     2,4
       END  
